%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/V%C3%A2n-S%C6%A1n-quan/poem-JwXu9XxGMyVZ2_m9EfHr_Q">Vân Sơn quan - 雲山關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-AqEVkg0YBflkFbuAXYlrbA">Hoàng Nguyễn Thự</a>)<br></div>	</div>
